TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Moment Matrix of the Two-Stage Least-Squares Estimator of Coefficients in Different Equations of a Complete System of Simultaneous Equations
AU  - Nagar, A. L.
AU  - Gupta, Y. P.
AB  - [In this article we analyze the moment matrix, to order 1/T^2(T being the number of observations), of the two-stage least-squares estimators of coefficients in two different equations which are part of a complete set of structural equations.]
