TY  - JOUR
TI  - Lindahl's Solution and the Core of an Economy with Public Goods
AU  - Foley, Duncan K.
AB  - [In an economy with an arbitrary number of consumers and an arbitrary number of commodities, some public and some private, I propose a generalization of Lindahl's equilibrium solution, and prove an existence theorem for it. A particular generalization of the "core" of an exchange equilibrium to an economy with public goods is proposed, and it is shown that a Lindahl equilibrium allocation is also a core allocation.]
